                                        <p><strong class="bold-info">Room Type:</strong><strong class="mainInfo"> Deluxe
                                                Room</strong></p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <p><strong class="bold-info">Email:</strong><strong class="mainInfo">
                                                tdorji@gmail.com</strong></p>
                                        <p><strong class="bold-info">Check out:</strong><strong class="mainInfo">
